nt of premature ejaculation [A177625].

Regardless, lidocaine is currently available as a relatively non-expensive generic medication that is written for in millions of prescriptions internationally on a yearly basis. It is even included in the World Health Organization''s List of Essential Medicines [L6055].', '["S01HA07", "D04AB01", "R02AD02", "C01BB01", "S02DA01", "N01BB52", "C05AD01", "N01BB02"]', '[]');
